{"type":"message","id":"6538e4ba","parentId":"ebaaa04d","timestamp":"2026-03-12T05:12:23.001Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问我能不能自己开启权限。根据AGENTS.md中的说明：\n\n\"### Disabled Tools\n\nThe following tool categories are currently disabled. If the owner requests functionality from a disabled category, inform them it can be enabled.\n\n**飞书插件工具（可按需开启）：**\n- **Task (任务) 工具:** `feishu_task_task`, `feishu_task_tasklist`, `feishu_task_comment`, `feishu_task_subtask`\n- **Task (任务) skill:** `feishu-task`\n...\"\n\n开启方式是编辑 openclaw.json。\n\n但是根据AGENTS.md的另一部分：\n\"**Ask first:**\n- Sending emails, tweets, public posts\n- Anything that leaves the machine\n- Anything you're uncertain about\"\n\n而且在Lark Integration部分：\n\"### Disabled Tools\n开启方式：\n1. 工具：编辑 `openclaw.json`，从 `tools.deny` 数组中移除对应工具名\n2. Skill：编辑 `openclaw.json`，将 `skills.entries` 中 `\"feishu-task\": { \"enabled\": false }` 改为 `true`\n3. 执行 `sh scripts/restart.sh` 重启生效\"\n\n这涉及到修改系统配置，我应该先问用户确认，因为：\n1. 这是配置变更\n2. 需要重启服务\n3. 可能影响现有功能\n\n我应该告诉用户我可以帮他开启，但需要确认。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我可以帮你开启，但需要确认一下：\n\n**开启后我会：**\n1. 修改 `openclaw.json` 启用任务工具和skill\n2. 重启服务使配置生效\n\n**影响：**\n- 重启过程中服务会短暂不可用（几秒钟）\n- 开启后我就能帮你查飞书任务、提醒员工了\n\n确认开启吗？ 🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":166,"output":364,"cacheRead":30522,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31052,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773292330285}}
