n1. 编辑 `openclaw.json`，从 `tools.deny` 数组中移除以下工具：\n   - `feishu_task_task`\n   - `feishu_task_tasklist`\n   - `feishu_task_comment`\n   - `feishu_task_subtask`\n2. 将 `skills.entries` 中的 `\"feishu-task\": { \"enabled\": false }` 改为 `true`\n3. 执行 `sh scripts/restart.sh` 重启生效\n\n开启后，我就能查询并返回完整的未完成任务列表了。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773292432642}]}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773292454825}}
